title: Can I change the default installation location for applications?
answer:
Yes. To change the default installation location for applications, go to Settings, and touch All > Storage > Default storage location. If you have a microSD card installed on your phone, the SD card option is available. Third-party applications will be installed to the default storage location you have selected.
